items.reviewContent:
Defected and unusable product.Pathetic Service. 

Bought this dispenser before Ramadan and found it to be defected as it was adding an odour which made water through it undrinkable. Initially I had a heated conversation with my water supplier as it was beyond my imagination that a product out of factory could be at fault. After realising I was wrong, I complained of the issue within the return policy time. However I was ensured the issue would be resolved. Being an avid user of Dawlance products I felt I should trust them, however this proved to be wrong.

Dispenser was taken the first time and returned after servicing only to find out the issue was still persistent. 

After several complaints, they took it again last week for inspection   , kept it at the service centre for a week and it arrived today filled with cockroaches in all portions.

Technicians havent found any fault and have returned it with cockroaches.

I guess dawlance isnt reliable anymore.
